he%20Israeli%20occupation's%20actions%20as%20a%20compounded%20crime%2C%20starting%20from%20the%20moment%20of%20Raddad's%20arrest%20and%20shooting%2C%20his%20use%20as%20a%20human%20shield%2C%20and%20the%20continued%20detention%20despite%20his%20severe%20health%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20described%20this%20incident%20as%20part%20of%20the%20unprecedented%20scale%20of%20crimes%20committed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20its%20genocidal%20campaign%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20and%20its%20ongoing%20aggression%20against%20Palestinians%20across%20all%20occupied%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20have%20been%20running%20high%20across%20the%20West%20Bank%20since%20Israel%20launched%20a%20military%20offensive%20against%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20that%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2040%2C400%20Palestinians%20since%20last%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20641%20Palestinians%20have%20since%20been%20killed%20and%20nearly%205%2C400%20others%20injured%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20Health%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20advisory%20opinion%20on%20July%2019%2C%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20declared%20Israel's%20decades-long%20occupation%20of%20Palestinian%20land%20unlawful%20and%20demanded%20the%20evacuation%20of%20all%20existing%20settlements%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20East%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724635260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F93ghint8_zaher-raddad_625x300_26_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpalestinian-prisoner-who-was-used-as-human-shield-by-israel-army-dies-6418172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20wounded%20Palestinian%20prisoner%20h