on%2C%20taking%20out%20thousands%20of%20Hezbollah%20missile%20launchers%20in%20what%20was%20called%20a%20preemptive%20strike%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20braced%20for%20an%20expanded%20conflagration%20that%20could%20involve%20Iran%20and%20its%20allied%20militias.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assault%20started%20at%205%20am%20local%20time%20and%20was%20based%2C%20Israeli%20officials%20said%2C%20on%20precise%20intelligence%20that%20Hezbollah%20was%20about%20to%20fire%20thousands%20of%20missiles%20at%20northern%20Israel%20as%20well%20as%20drones%20at%20a%20key%20intelligence%20centre%20just%20north%20of%20Tel%20Aviv%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20its%20commander%20in%20July.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20declared%20a%2048-hour%20state%20of%20emergency%20and%20shut%20its%20main%20airport%20for%20several%20hours%2C%20with%20numerous%20foreign%20airlines%20cancelling%20flights.%20Hezbollah%20responded%20by%20firing%20more%20than%20200%20projectiles%2C%20according%20to%20Israel%2C%20although%20officials%20said%20very%20limited%20damage%20was%20caused.%20One%20Israeli%20soldier%20was%20killed%20by%20falling%20debris%2C%20while%20three%20deaths%20were%20reported%20in%20Lebanon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Hezbollah%20had%20successfully%20executed%20an%20attack%20on%20targets%20in%20central%20Israel%2C%20the%20tit-for-tat%20fighting%20that's%20been%20simmering%20on%20the%20border%20area%20for%2010%20months%20may%20have%20exploded%20into%20wider%20warfare.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20hope%20is%20that%20the%20events%20of%20last%20night%20do%20not%20spill%20out%20into%20an%20escalation%20that%20leads%20to%20regional%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20told%20reporters%20on%20Sunday%20evening%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20time%20being%2C%20at%20least%2C%20a%20relative%20calm%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20huge%20success%20that%20we%20detected%20the%20plans%20and%20now%20there%20is%20the%20possibility%20for%20both%20sides%20not%20to%20escalate%20this%20very%20complex%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20retired%20Brigadier%20General%20Ilan%20Biton%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20of%20defense%20for%20Israel's%20air%20force.%20Both%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%20announced%20that%20for%20the%20moment%2C%20their%20operations%20were%20over%20-%20despite%20ongoing%20low-level%20fighting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20reopened%20its%20airport%20and%20eased%20restrictions%20on%20public%20gatherings%20imposed%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%20Israel's%20military%20spokesman%2C%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20said%20there%20was%20no%20damage%20to%20any%20Israeli%20military%20base.%20The%20Israeli%20army%20didn't%20reimpose%20safety%20restrictions%20on%20the%20population%20on%20Sunday%20night%2C%20indicating%20it%20didn't%20expect%20another%20attack%20imminently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20negotiations%20in%20Cairo%20aimed%20at%20establishing%20a%20cease-fire%20in%20Gaza%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20militia%20Hamas%20commenced%20as%20planned%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20a%20Hamas%20delegation%20left%20Cairo%20on%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20Osama%20Hamdan%2C%20a%20spokesman%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20group%2C%20said%20Israel%20has%20%26quot%3Bset%20new%20conditions%20for%20a%20cease-fire%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bis%20still%20procrastinating%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20the%20group's%20Telegram%20account.%20In%20a%20dig%20at%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%2C%20he%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bplanting%20false%20hope%20by%20talking%20about%20an%20imminent%20agreement%20for%20electoral%20purposes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20are%20set%20to%20continue%20at%20lower%20levels%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20bridge%20gaps%20between%20the%20parties%2C%20the%20Associated%20Press%20reported%2C%20citing%20a%20US%20official%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%20The%20official%20said%20the%20recent%20talks%20have%20been%20constructive%20and%20the%20parties%20are%20working%20to%20reach%20an%20implementable%20agreement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderscoring%20'Consequences'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20exchange%20with%20Hezbollah%20%26quot%3Bis%20more%20likely%20to%20aid%20than%20complicate%20the%20cease-fire%20talks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike%20Singh%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20Washington%20Institute.%20%26quot%3BBy%20sending%20a%20message%20that%20Israel%20is%20willing%20and%20able%20to%20escalate%2C%20and%20that%20Washington%20will%20back%20it%20when%20it%20does%20so%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20have%20underscored%20the%20consequences%20for%20Hamas%2C%20Hezbollah%20and%20Iran%20of%20continuing%20to%20refuse%20a%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20said%20its%20attack%20on%20Israel%20was%20planned%20as%20the%20start%20of%20retaliation%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20its%20commander%20Fuad%20Shukr%20on%20July%2030%20in%20Beirut's%20southern%20suburbs.%20The%20group%20said%20it%20fired%20more%20than%20320%20missiles%2C%20followed%20up%20by%20drones%2C%20to%20target%2011%20army%20barracks%20and%20military%20sites%20in%20northern%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mossad%20intelligence%20service's%20base%20in%20Glilot%20was%20the%20main%20target%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20Hezbollah%20Secretary%20General%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20said%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20convened%20a%20security%20cabinet%20meeting%20Sunday%20and%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdetermined%20to%20do%20everything%20to%20defend%20our%20country%2C%20to%20return%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20north%20securely%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20to%20continue%20upholding%20a%20simple%20rule%3A%20Whoever%20harms%20us%20-%20we%20will%20harm%20them.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELieutenant%20Colonel%20Nadav%20Shoshani%2C%20an%20Israeli%20military%20spokesman%2C%20noted%20that%20Israeli%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20and%20US%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20spoke%20by%20phone%20over%20the%20weekend.%20He%20declined%20to%20say%20whether%20the%20US%20was%20given%20advance%20warning%20of%20Sunday's%20attack%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20an%20Israeli%20operation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20Support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20stepped%20up%20its%20naval%20and%20air%20defense%20presence%20in%20the%20region%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20Iran%20and%20its%20allies%20not%20to%20increase%20hostilities.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Israel%20had%20informed%20the%20US%20in%20advance%20of%20its%20plans%20to%20hit%20at%20Hezbollah%2C%20Sullivan%2C%20the%20national%20security%20adviser%2C%20sidestepped%20the%20question.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20speak%20directly%20to%20the%20conversations%20that%20unfolded%20yesterday%2C%20other%20than%20to%20say%20there%20was%20continuous%20communication%2C%20and%20we%20have%20been%20tracking%20the%20threat%20of%20Hezbollah%20attacks%20against%20Israel%20for%20some%20time%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20fresh%20US%20statements%20Sunday%20affirming%20support%20for%20Israel's%20right%20to%20defense%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20Hezbollah%20is%20a%20setback%20for%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20diplomacy%2C%20which%20has%20been%20laser-focused%20on%20de-escalation%26quot%3B%20and%20on%20the%20search%20for%20a%20cease-fire%20in%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20Merissa%20Khurma%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20program%20at%20the%20Wilson%20Center%20in%20Washington.%20%26quot%3BIn%20private%2C%20the%20past%20ten-plus%20months%20have%20showcased%20various%20ebbs%20and%20flows%20in%20US-Israeli%20relations%2C%20and%20certainly%20a%20significant%20rise%20in%20tensions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20it%20raises%20doubts%20among%20regional%20allies%20about%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20the%20US%20still%20has%20leverage%20over%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Hezbollah%20have%20been%20trading%20fire%20along%20the%20border%20since%20October%2C%20when%20the%20Lebanese%20organization%20entered%20the%20fray%20in%20support%20of%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%20Israeli%20strikes%20have%20killed%20at%20least%20500%20people%20since%20then%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Hezbollah%20fighters.%20In%20Israel%2C%20roughly%2030%20soldiers%20and%2018%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20Hezbollah%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventing%20the%20skirmishes%20from%20escalating%20even%20further%20has%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20international%20diplomatic%20efforts%20to%20ease%20tension%20across%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20July%2030%20killed%20Hezbollah's%20military%20chief%20in%20Beirut%2C%20Iran%20blamed%20Israel%20for%20killing%20the%20head%20of%20Hamas'%20political%20office%2C%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20in%20Tehran.%20Iran%20has%20vowed%20to%20retaliate%20but%20it%20has%20also%20said%20it%20would%20do%20so%20on%20its%20own%20timetable.%20Israel%20has%20repeatedly%20warned%20it%20not%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Netanyahu%20warned%20Hezbollah%20and%20Iran%20that%20the%20latest%20attack%20isn't%20%26quot%3Bthe%20end%20of%20the%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Banother%20step%20on%20the%20way%20to%20changing%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20north%2C%20and%20return%20our%20residents%20safely%20to%20their%20homes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvacuations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20mediate%20between%20Lebanon%20and%20Israel%20to%20reach%20a%20compromise%20over%20border%20disputes.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Israelis%20and%20Lebanese%20have%20been%20evacuated%20from%20the%20border%20area%20due%20to%20the%20fighting%2C%20and%20Israel%20wants%20Hezbollah%20to%20move%20its%20fighters%20away%20from%20the%20border%20to%20allow%20its%20citizens%20to%20return.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20which%20is%20backed%20by%20Iran%20and%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%2C%20says%20it%20will%20continue%20hostilities%20with%20Israel%20until%20the%20country%20agrees%20to%20a%20cease-fire%20in%20Gaza%20with%20Hamas%2C%20also%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20group%20by%20the%20US%20and%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20enclave%20began%20on%20Oct.%207%20after%20Hamas%20militants%2C%20supported%20by%20Iran%2C%20invaded%20Israel%20and%20killed%201%2C200%20people%20and%20abducted%20others.%20Israel's%20retaliation%20in%20Gaza%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2040%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Hamas%20health%20officials%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724635020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmh4q08o_israel-hezbollah-afp_625x300_26_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmiddle-east-on-edge-day-after-israel-hezbollah-exchange-heavy-fire-6418371%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20100%20Israeli%20warplanes%20swooped%20over%20southern%20Lebanon%2C%20taking%20out%20thousands%20of%20Hezbollah%20missile%20launchers%20in%20what%20was%20called%20a%20preemptive%20strike%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20braced%20for%20an%20expanded%20conflagration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmiddle-east-on-edge-day-after-israel-hezbollah-exchange-heavy-fire-6418371%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ben's%20influence%20over%20Jennifer%20Lopez's%20documentary%2