20Opposition%20in%20Kerala%20has%20asked%20for%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20revelations%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20chief%20minister%20on%20record%20said%20that%20if%20they%20come%20with%20specific%20complaints%2C%20the%20process%20will%20be%20set%20in%20motion.%20He%20has%20already%20said%20it.%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20anything%20because%20I%20do%20not%20deal%20with%20the%20subject%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20would%20like%20to%20trust%20what%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20said%2C%20that%20if%20the%20victims%20come%20forward%20and%20they%20file%20a%20complaint%20against%20those%20perpetrators%2C%20then%20the%20process%20of%20law%20will%20be%20set%20in%20motion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20form%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%2C%20led%20by%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%2C%20to%20investigate%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20recent%20interviews%20and%20statements%20from%20several%20women%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20detailing%20the%20hardships%20they%20have%20faced%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20convened%20a%20meeting%20with%20senior%20police%20officials%20here%20on%20Sunday%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official%20release%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20decided%20to%20form%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%2C%20led%20by%20IGP%20G%20Sparjan%20Kumar%2C%20to%20look%20into%20these%20complaints%20and%20revelations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Hema%20Committee%20Report%20last%20week%2C%20which%20revealed%20numerous%20instances%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20in%20the%20film%20industry%2C%20many%20women%20have%20come%20forward%2C%20reporting%20experiences%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20in%20the%20industry.T