%20Kashmir%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20after%20a%20meeting%20of%20its%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20committee%20had%20met%20to%20finalise%20the%20party's%20candidates%20for%20the%20coming%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20--%20which%20is%20taking%20place%20after%20a%20decade.%20The%20final%20list%20of%20candidates%20is%20expected%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20were%20joined%20by%20other%20CEC%20members%2C%20including%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20as%20they%20discussed%20the%20matter%20with%20party%20leaders%20from%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20local%20leaders%20had%20held%20a%20long%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Nadda%20and%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20among%20others%2C%20to%20narrow%20down%20the%20list%20of%20probables.%20The%20meet%20also%20included%20a%20strategy%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20last%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20going%20into%20polls%20without%20any%20strong%20local%20pre-poll%20alliance.%20But%20sources%20said%20the%20party%20will%20extend%20support%20to%20regional%20parties%20and%20Independent%20candidates%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20which%20will%20begin%20in%20September%20and%20will%20be%20held%20in%20three%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20over%20its%20comments%20on%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party's%20alliance%20with%20Omar%20Abdullah's%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20hypocrisy%2C%20Mr%20Surjewala%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20partnered%20both%20National%20Conference%20and%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20we%20ever%20asked%20the%20BJP%20whom%20they%20will%20ally%20with%3F%20Then%20why%20is%20the%20BJP%20questioning%20us%3F%20Had%20the%20BJP%20not%20allied%20with%20the%20National%20Conference%20or%20PDP%20in%20the%20past%3F%20They%20did.%20When%20you%20have%20done%20this%20before%2C%20why%20are%20you%20questioning%20us%20about%20our%20alliance%3F%26quot%3B%20ANI%20quoted%20Mr%20Surjewala%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202014%20election%2C%20when%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20a%20full-fledged%20state%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%2025%20seats.%20It%20had%20formed%20government%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20PDP%2C%20which%20collapsed%20in%202018%2C%20after%20which%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20came%20under%20President's%20Rule.%20In%202019%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status%20was%20revoked%20and%20the%20state%20was%20split%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20making%20an%20all-out%20effort%20to%20fend%20off%20the%20challenge%20from%20a%20resurgent%20Congress%2C%20and%20its%20ally%20the%20National%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2090-member%20assembly%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20going%20to%20polls%20in%20three%20phases%20--%20September%2018%20and%2025%20and%20October%201.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20be%20held%20on%20October%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20BJP%20CEC%20meeting%20is%20scheduled%20for%20August%2029%20to%20strategise%20for%20Haryana%20polls.%20The%20BJP%20is%20facing%20a%20strong%20challenge%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%20Haryana%2C%20where%20it%20has%20been%20in%20power%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724610840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2oc3s9kc_bjp-cec-meeting-jk-_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-amit-shah-at-party-panel-meet-to-decide-on-j-k-poll-candidates-6417203%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20win%2066%20of%20the%2090%20seats%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20after%20a%20meeting%20