ider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-deepfake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemerging%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20create%20realistic%20images%20and%20videos%2C%20including%20deepfake%20pornography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20I%20like%20being%2014%20and%20making%20a%20Twitter%20account%20because%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20and%20seeing%20dirty%20edited%20content%20of%20me%20as%20a%20child%3F%20No.%20It's%20terrifying.%20It's%20corrupt.%20It's%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20child%20actor%2C%20who%20rose%20to%20fame%20starring%20in%20the%20Disney%20Channel%20series%20%26quot%3BStuck%20in%20the%20Middle%26quot%3B%20and%20CW%20comedy%20%26quot%3BJane%20the%20Virgin%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20she%20was%20told%20to%20sign%20up%20to%20Twitter%20to%20build%20her%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jenna%20Ortega%20in%20Stuck%20in%20the%20middle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65141a0c1c099d0019ad2c0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJenna%20Ortega%20rose%20to%20fame%20as%20a%20child%20star%20on%20Disney%20Channel's%20%26quot%3BStuck%20in%20the%20Middle.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3EEric%20McCandless%20%2F%20Disney%20Channel%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20first%20%E2%80%94%20actually%20the%20first%20D.M.%20that%20I%20ever%20opened%20myself%20when%20I%20was%2012%20was%20an%20unsolicited%20photo%20of%20a%20man's%20genitals%2C%20and%20that%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20what%20was%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtega%20said%20that%20she%20ended%20up%20deleting%20the%20app%20%26quot%3Babout%20two%2C%20three%20years%20ago%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Binflux%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20images%20and%20photos%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20receiving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20disgusting%2C%20and%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20bad.%20It%20made%20me%20feel%20uncomfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BAnyway%2C%20that's%20why%20I%20deleted%20it%2C%20because%20I%20couldn't%20say%20anything%20without%20seeing%20something%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtega%20isn't%20the%20first%20person%20to%20be%20targeted%20by%20those%20creating%20and%20disseminating%20realistic%20AI%20porn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Taylor%20Swift's%20likeness%20was%20used%20in%20a%20series%20of%20sexually%20explicit%20posts%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-nude-deepfake-artificial-intelligence-law-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewent%20viral%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20ended%20up%20temporarily%20blocking%20searches%20for%20the%20singer%20as%20a%20safety%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20company%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BPosting%20Non-Consensual%20Nudity%20(NCN)%20images%20is%20strictly%20prohibited%20on%20X%20and%20we%20have%20a%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20towards%20such%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20teams%20are%20actively%20removing%20all%20identified%20images%20and%20taking%20appropriate%20actions%20against%20the%20accounts%20responsible%20for%20posting%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20led%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-nude-deepfake-artificial-intelligence-law-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalls%20for%20new%20legislation%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20combat%20the%20threats%20posed%20by%20deepfakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Joseph%20Morelle%20proposed%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20make%20it%20a%20crime%20to%20intentionally%20share%20or%20threaten%20to%20share%20digitally%20altered%20images%20of%20an%20individual%20engaging%20in%20sexually%20explicit%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20titled%20the%20Preventing%20Deepfakes%20of%20Intimate%20Images%20Act%2C%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20House%20Committee%20on%20the%20Judiciary%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F118th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F3106%3Fs%3D1%26r%3D64%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20further%20action%20has%20yet%20been%20taken%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20the%20devastating%20impacts%20intimate%20deepfakes%20images%20have%20had%20on%20everyone%20from%20young%20schoolgirls%20to%20world-wide%20celebrities%2C%26quot%3B%20Morelle%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmorelle.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Fcongressman-joe-morelle-announces-new-support-his-legislation-stop-deepfake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20topic.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20responsibility%20to%20take%20decisive%20action%20that%20puts%20a%20stop%20to%20these%20heinous%20crimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjenna-ortega-twitter-explicit-ai-images-actor-x-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724608016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cb555b43b5e59d16b4f989%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjenna-ortega-twitter-explicit-ai-images-actor-x-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ortega%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Interview%26quot%3B%20podcast%20that%20she%20shut%20down%20her%20Twitter%20account%20after%20an%20%26quot%3Binflux%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20images%20and%20photos.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ecrosbie%40businessinsider.com%20(Eve%20Crosbie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjenna-ortega-twitter-explicit-ai-images-actor-x-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Man%20Fin