the%20field%20of%20healthcare%20and%20also%20practiced%20as%20a%20physician%20in%20Tuscaloosa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20many%20are%20aware%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20we%20have%20been%20informed%20of%20Dr.%20Ramesh%20Peramsetty's%20passing.%20The%20Peramsetty%20family%20ask%20for%20us%20to%20give%20them%20privacy%20as%20they%20grieve%20his%20passing.%20They%20have%20received%20abundant%20outpouring%20of%20love%20and%20faith.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20honor%20him%20as%20he%20would%20want%20us%20to%20do.%20Thank%20you%20for%20your%20understanding%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Crimson%20Care%20Network%20Team%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post.%20(sic)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Crimson%20Care%20Network%20said%20its%20team%20%26quot%3Bis%20prepared%20to%20make%20more%20statements%20within%20the%20next%20few%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Was%20Dr%20Ramesh%20Babu%20Peramsetty%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Peramsetty%20graduated%20from%20the%20Medical%20College%20of%20Wisconsin%2C%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20Medical%20College%20in%201986%2C%20according%20to%20his%20Wedmd%20page.%20He%20had%2038%20years%20of%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20worked%20in%20Tuscaloosa%20and%20four%20other%20locations%20and%20was%20specialised%20in%20Emergency%20Medicine%20and%20Family%20Medicine%2C%20it%20says.%20He%20was%20also%20affiliated%20with%20Diploma%20in%20Child%20Health%20(DCH)%20Regional%20Medical%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20local%20reports%2C%20a%20street%20in%20Tuscaloosa%20was%20named%20after%20him%20due%20to%20his%20significant%20contributions%20in%20the%20medical%20profession.%20He%20also%20did%20extensive%20work%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20and%20also%20received%20awards%20for%20the%20same%2C%20reports%20suggest.%20He%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20two%20sons%20and%20two%20daughters%20and%20all%20are%20settled%20in%20the%20US%2C%20as%20per%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20donated%20Rs%2014%20lakh%20to