Cp%3EInitially%2C%20their%20interactions%20were%20limited%20to%20casual%20pleasantries.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20conductor%20became%20more%20familiar%2C%20touching%20her%20arm%20and%20asking%20about%20what%20she%20was%20watching%20on%20her%20phone.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20requested%20her%20phone%20number%2C%20which%20she%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20described%20an%20incident%20where%2C%20after%20she%20refused%20to%20give%20her%20number%2C%20the%20conductor%20blocked%20her%20way%20when%20she%20tried%20to%20leave%20the%20bus%20at%20her%20stop.%20%26quot%3BSo%20today%20when%20he%20came%20to%20say%20hi%20I%20just%20nodded%20and%20turned%20my%20head%2C%20however%20when%20my%20stop%20came%20he%20was%20blocking%20the%20way%20for%20me%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20seat%20(I%20was%20sitting%20near%20the%20window)%20and%20the%20lady%20sitting%20next%20to%20me%20had%20to%20push%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recounted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20polite%20responses%2C%20she%20mentioned%20that%20the%20conductor%2C%20who%20is%20likely%20in%20his%20late%20forties%20or%20early%20fifties%2C%20continued%20to%20make%20her%20uncomfortable.%20She%20concluded%20her%20post%20by%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BShould%20I%20be%20concerned%2C%20or%20am%20I%20just%20looking%20into%20things%20too%20much%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20viral%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FKochi%2Fcomments%2F1ez4ips%2Fis_the_bus_conductor_being_creepy_or_just_friendly%2F%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20bus%20conductor%20being%20creepy%20or%20just%20friendly%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FSensitive-Ninja2324%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FSensitive-Ninja2324%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FKochi%2F%5C%22%3EKochi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES