bitter%20at%20all%20because%20it%20used%20a%20blonde%20roast%20and%20was%20topped%20with%20the%20vanilla-sweet-cream%20cold%20foam.%20Instead%2C%20the%20coffee%20flavor%20I%20love%20was%20balanced%20with%20some%20sweetness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%247.70%2C%20this%20drink%20came%20in%20at%20the%20mid-range%20price%20point%20of%20all%20the%20barista-recommended%20Starbucks%20drinks%20I%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFinally%2C%20I%20tested%20a%20nuttier%20version%20of%20a%20white%20mocha%20recommended%20by%20barista%20Nelly.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starbucks%20drink%20from%20Nelly%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bbba7eb4912df3ae1b54e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fifth%20barista%20I%20spoke%20to%20customized%20an%20iced%20white-chocolate%20mocha.%20%3Cp%3EPaige%20Bennett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENelly%2C%20the%20fifth%20barista%20I%20talked%20to%2C%20recommended%20an%20iced%20white-chocolate%20mocha%20with%20several%20adaptations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20drink%20started%20as%20an%20iced%20white%20mocha%2C%20subbing%20the%20signature%20two%20shots%20of%20espresso%20for%20a%20triple%20shot%20of%20blonde%20espresso%20roast%2C%20swapping%20two%20of%20the%20four%20pumps%20of%20white-chocolate%20mocha%20sauce%20for%20two%20pumps%20of%20toffee-nut%20syrup%2C%20and%20nixing%20the%20whipped%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20the%20biggest%20fan%20of%20white%20chocolate%2C%20but%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20give%20it%20a%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20nutty%2C%20toffee%20syrup%20balanced%20out%20the%20sweetness%20of%20the%20white%20chocolate.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starbucks%20drink%20from%20Nelly%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bbba7d955b01c3294e43c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20toffee-n