%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20arrow%20has%20left%20the%20bow%20and%20it%20goes%20in%20a%20certain%20direction%2C%20post%20which%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20move.%20Even%20if%20we%20asked%20them%20to%20improve%20certain%20skills%2C%20there%20was%20something%20stopping%20them.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20wasting%20my%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harpreet%20shares%20candidly%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20selling%20the%20company%20to%20Aon%20Hewitt%20in%202016%2C%20he%20spent%20a%20few%20years%20following%20his%20passion%20of%20mountaineering%20and%20running%20ultra%20marathons.%20However%2C%20while%20doing%20this%2C%20he%20missed%20out%20on%20spending%20precious%20time%20with%20his%20infant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20left%20him%20wondering%20whether%20he%20was%20making%20the%20right%20choices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20spoke%20to%20any%20older%20person%2C%20the%20one%20regret%20they%20had%20was%20not%20spending%20enough%20time%20with%20their%20children.%20They%20always%20said%20that%20they%20never%20realised%20when%20their%20children%20grew%20up.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20have%20a%20similar%20regret%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harpreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20the%20consequences%20of%20his%20actions%2C%20he%20started%20spending%20more%20time%20at%20home%20with%20his%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20first%20few%20years%20of%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20life%20along%20with%20a%20parent%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20it%2C%20Suman%20Khanna%2C%20counselling%20psychologist%20and%20founder%2C%20Mind%20Unwind%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20says%20that%20this%20is%20when%20they%20start%20understanding%20the%20world%20and%20environment%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20few%20years%20of%20life%2C%20especially%20the%20first%20six%20months%2C%20a%20child%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20ask%20for%20something.%20The%20presence%20of%20a%20parent%20to%20