h%20impurities%20like%20baking%20soda%20or%20washing%20powder.%20Pure%20jaggery%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20will%20not%20react%20in%20this%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20rising%20cases%20of%20food%20adulteration%20and%20growing%20concerns%20over%20food%20safety%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20important%20than%20ever%20to%20be%20vigilant.%20Taking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352550%2Fhow-to-check-spices-purity-at-home-adulteration-indian-red-chili-powder-hing-turmeric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejust%20a%20few%20minutes%20to%20perform%20these%20simple%20tests%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20you%20ensure%20that%20the%20salt%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20jaggery%20in%20your%20kitchen%20are%20pure%2C%20safeguarding%20your%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftoxicslink.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FPress%2520Release_English_Microplastics%2520In%2520Salt%2520and%2520Sugar_Toxics%2520Link%2520Study.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEating%20Lots%20Of%20%E2%80%98Sugar%20%26amp%3B%20Salt%E2%80%99%3F%20You%20Are%20Eating%20Lots%20of%20%E2%80%98Plastics%E2%80%99%20Too%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20Toxics%20Link%2C%20Published%20on%2013%20August%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724422529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362783%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20rising%20concerns%20over%20food%20adulteration%2C%20here%20are%20four%20DIY%20tests%20to%20detect%20impurities%20in%20salt%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20jaggery%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22