yesight%20had%20done%20more%20than%20fluster%20him%3B%20it%20had%20also%20threatened%20to%20put%20a%20stopper%20on%20his%20career%20goals.%20He%20could%20no%20longer%20hope%20to%20study%20at%20the%20universities%20he%20was%20looking%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Bhachau%20(a%20city%20under%20the%20Kachchh%20district)%20native%20admits%20that%20no%20adversity%20could%20make%20education%20take%20a%20backseat.%20%E2%80%9CI%20began%20travelling%20around%20Gujarat%3B%20to%20Baroda%2C%20Jamnagar%20and%20Ahmedabad.%20I%20began%20studying%20at%20the%20colleges%20there%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324715%2Fmeet-annie-worlds-first-self-learning-braille-device-that-also-acts-as-a-personal-tutor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20learning%20braille%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20The%20reason%20to%20set%20his%20sights%20beyond%20Kachchh%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20because%20his%20home%20city%20did%20not%20cater%20to%20blind%20persons.%20In%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20Laljibhai%20obtained%20his%20graduation%20degree%20in%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%201975%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20home%20city%2C%20it%20was%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20learning.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20met%20so%20many%20blind%20people%20who%20did%20not%20have%20the%20same%20opportunities%20I%20had%20had%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20This%20thought%20led%20Laljibhai%20to%20formally%20register%20what%20had%20started%20as%20an%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20%E2%80%94%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home_11zon-1723031030.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20old%20age%20home%20has%20seen%20over%20500%20senior%20citizens%20to%20date.%20These%20include%20both%20di