2%3EFarish%20and%20Calvin%20are%20growing%20exotic%20crops%20such%20as%20lettuce%2C%20basil%2C%20kale%20and%20parsley%20using%20AI.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20focussed%20on%20integrating%20advanced%20technology%20and%20automation%20to%20enhance%20crop%20quality%2C%20taste%2C%20and%20production%20efficiency%20while%20reducing%20operational%20costs.%20They%20built%20their%20own%203D%20pipes%20to%20grow%20crops%20vertically.%20%E2%80%9COur%20patented%20pipes%20allow%20precise%20control%20of%20environmental%20variables%20like%20light%20spectrum%20and%20temperature%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Farish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20software%20inputs%2C%20the%20system%20irrigates%20and%20maintains%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20pH%2C%20water%20conductivity%2C%20air%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20and%20all%20other%20parameters%20to%20provide%20an%20ideal%20environment%20suitable%20for%20plant%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20used%20special%20spectrum%20lights%20that%20mimic%20sunlight%20but%20emit%20the%20exact%20wavelengths%20required%20for%20plant%20growth.%20An%20ideal%20plant%20requires%20light%20wavelengths%20between%20600%20and%20700%20nanometers%20for%20photosynthesis.%20For%20human%20eyes%2C%20they%20look%20purplish%20blue%20in%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Calvin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20traditional%20farming%20methods%2C%20the%20AI-enabled%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356971%2Fhydroponics-farming-without-soil-sustainable-agriculture-farmer-increases-income-solar-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponic%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Emethod%20not%20only%20saves%2095%20percent%20of%20water%20as%20it%20is%20reused%20in%20the%20setup%20but%20also%20brings%20operational%20costs%20to%2050%20percent.%20This%2C%20Farish%20says%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20make%20agriculture%20more%20sustainable%20and%20profitable%20for%20farm