they%20have%20built%20farms%20for%20about%2010%20agri-entrepreneurs%20and%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Krop%20AI%20won%20the%20Karnataka%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Idea2POC%2FElevate%2F2023%20grant%20in%20the%20biotech%20sector.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20incubated%20with%20the%20AIC%20Nitte%20incubation%20centre%20under%20the%20Startup%20India%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20made%20a%20total%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20with%20a%2040%20percent%20gross%20profit%20on%20manufacturing%20of%20farm%20stations.%20This%20year%2C%20they%20project%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20our%20technology%20allows%20us%20to%20grow%20crops%20indoors%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20perfect%20weather%20conditions%20for%20better%20harvests.%20Our%20plants%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357394%2Fhydroponics-farmers-increase-income-yield-reduce-water-wastage-india-saffron-strawberries-soil-less-farming-technique%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThis%2520method%2520of%2520farming%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520hydroponics%2Cstart%252C%2520we%2520have%2520you%2520covered.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20sun%20and%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20without%20compromising%20the%20taste.%20We%20are%20glad%20that%20within%20two%20years%20of%20time%2C%20we%20have%20not%20only%20been%20able%20to%20work%20on%20our%20patented%20technology%20but%20also%20revolutionised%20farming%20solutions%20for%20farmers.%20We%20hope%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20work%20and%20reach%20to%20small%20and%20medium%20income%20growers%20so%20that%20they%20can%20benefit%20from%20our%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Farish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Calvin%20Aranha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724062679000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%